headline: Trimble (TRMB) Expands Sales Footprint With New Technology Outlet at Martin Equipment
summary: Trimble (TRMB) has recently expanded its business by partnering with Martin Equipment in Goodfield, Illinois, to establish a new Trimble Technology Outlet. This move, part of Trimble's civil construction distribution strategy, likely supports the company's share price increase of 10% over the last quarter. headline: Announcing Trimble Dimensions 2025: Engage the Future of Work Now
summary: Trimble (Nasdaq: TRMB) announced today the return of its flagship user conference, Trimble Dimensions 2025: trimble.com/dimensions. This premier event, focused on connecting the physical and digital worlds to transform industries, will take place November 10-12, 2025, at The Venetian Resort in Las Vegas.
